{"tid":731183,"cid":35,"subCid":0,"title":"CLS CS屋村拉光纖亂尻咁嗡","createTime":"2018-07-06T04:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-06T09:52:31.000Z","uid":159074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6fc66549a681cc77c5a09cd8c19782a17c063f62","tid":731183,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:10:37.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n我用開網上爬既電話線寬頻<br />\n因為所有既電訊商都當舊客係狗既關係想轉<br />\n打在去某間電訊商諗住轉<br />\n<br />\n我同個CS講到好清楚話唔用光纖 因為要拉線 唔想拉<br />\n佢就話試下 咁我都比師傅上黎安裝<br />\n<br />\n之後個師傅黎到搞左好耐話要拉線<br />\n咁我地就拒絕左唔裝<br />\n<br />\n見事未完<br />\n<br />\n過左幾日<br />\n個CS知道安裝唔成功佢再打黎話派個資深D既師傅<br />\n上到黎 <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">屌你老母 同一個人黎既喂</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n師傅都好有禮貌話我地屋企一定要拉線 之後就走左<br />\n<br />\n事隔2年<br />\n又係個間電訊商既CS打黎SALE<br />\n我都係果句:唔拉線<br />\n佢就話依加有新技術可以向機房電話線位隊條光纖入黎<br />\n<br />\n真係唔想哂時間<br />\n我覺得佢都係亂尻咁嗡所以REJRCT左<br />\n<br />\nCLS CS<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a448c8b0c67340a65a7cd34f29de3c84b636688","tid":731183,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:18:00.000Z","msg":"點解CS咁鐘意尻UP<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65f1b1a34b0f1d0e75ce294a9695885005d6654b","tid":731183,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T04:27:14.000Z","msg":"尻嗡完上到黎唔成功安置咁有咩謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4596a5444abea28464ec21f8bf98dbcfad1429cf","tid":731183,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-06T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17cf198dcbce3ce20a7c70ca9726b6068e45215b","tid":731183,"uid":159074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim